                <source>The following tags do not exist in the source text:<br/><ul><li>{0}</li></ul>This is how to solve this error:<br/><ul><li>Click “OK” to close this window</li><li>Press ESC to leave the segment without saving</li><li>Reopen the segment</li></ul>Re-apply your changes.</source>
